com.misc.common.moplaf.time.continuous

Interface StockChange

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, EventsProvider, EventsProviderAbstract, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, com.misc.common.moplaf.propagator.ObjectWithPropagatorFunctionAdapter
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StockChangeImpl

    public interface StockChange
extends EventsProvider
    A representation of the model object 'Stock Change'. A change of Amount spread in a given interval of time. The amount of the Distribution increases with a given Slope during the given time interval

    The following features are supported:

    • Start
    • End
    • Slope
    • Start Event
    • End Event
    See Also:
    ContinuousPackage.getStockChange()
